License: GPL (>= 2)
Imports: lme4 (>= 1.0)
Description: This package enables researchers to calculate power for cluster randomized trials (CRTs) comparing
  two means, two proportions, or two counts. In addition, this package calculates power for cluster randomized 
  crossover trials by employing a simulation-based approach.
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
